                             aria-labelledby="headingOne"
                             data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                Yes, the Android operating system for mobiles is owned and maintained by Google. But it is open
                                source and is supported by many other developers.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed"
                                    type="button"
                                    data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                    data-bs-target="#collapseTwo"
                                    aria-expanded="false"
                                    aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                Is it expensive to build Android mobile applications?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseTwo"
                             class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                             aria-labelledby="headingTwo"
                             data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                Android is one of the most cost-effective mobile building platforms out there. And in fact, it is
                                pretty cheap to build Android mobile applications.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
